'''''Return of the Jedi Winter Special''''' was a comic book released in the United Kingdom that reprinted Marvel Comics stories published earlier in the [[Star Wars (Marvel UK)|Marvel Star Wars UK]] series. The reprints were the stories originally released in the US as [[Star Wars (1977) 16|''Star Wars'' (1977) 16]] and [[Star Wars (1977) 17|''Star Wars'' (1977) 17]]

